name: Hebei General Metal Netting
overview:
Hebei General Metal Wire Mesh Co., Ltd! Professionally engaged in wire mesh production and export, Xinjia can provide customers with full range of wire mesh and wire products. Located in Anping County, the well-known Wire Mesh Land of China, we enjoy great advantages in developing new products and producing wire mesh products at competitive prices.

We mainly produce and offer Stainless Steel Wire Mesh, Wire Cloth in Black Iron & Brass, Wire Mesh Finished Filter Discs, Filter Elements, Wire Mesh Fencing Series, Wire Mesh for Battery, Welded Wire Mesh, Hexagonal Wire Netting, Expanded mesh, Perforated mesh, Galvanized Iron Wire, Tie Wire, Stainless Steel Wire and Other Wire Mesh Products.

Our products are available in a complete range of specifications and with excellent quality. The products have been exporting to U.S.A, Australia, Japan, Mexico, Malaysia, Egypt, Singapore, etc.

Hebei General Metal Wire Mesh Co., Ltd has advanced equipments, advanced technology and technical skill. The products are carefully examined and administrated in order to meet the needs of customers.

Please do not hesitate to contact with us for more information.
